Bug Description
If a hostile mob targets the player before using vanish, the mob will continue trying to attack the player even after the player has vanished.

Steps to Reproduce

Let a hostile mob target the player.
Use /vanish.
Observe the mob's behavior.
Expected Behavior
Hostile mobs should stop targeting the player after the player uses /vanish.

Actual Behavior
Hostile mobs continue attempting to attack the player even after the player has vanished.

